% Fourth Section %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
\section*{How to be successful in this course}
Successful students:
\begin{enumerate}
\item \textbf{Keep up w/ the material} - reading the chapter before class is necessary to understand the material.
\item \textbf{Are engaged} - attend class, be prepared, ask questions, and seek my help if you are having trouble with the material (see point 6).
\item \textbf{Complete  HW assignments on time} - your homework is a good preview of exam material and they are worth 30\% of your grade.
\item \textbf{Read and re-read the syllabus for any questions about the course }- it's a guide created for you to navigate the course successfully. 
\item \textbf{Check FIU Emails} - I communicate with the class this way concerning updates about the course. You're responsible for the emails I send to you.
\item \textbf{Consult with me about any issues regarding the course} - I cannot help you if you do not let me know beforehand.
\end{enumerate}

